snippet.title: Sokolab | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
#afilgames #sokolab

SokoLab is a Sokoban game where you play as a cute robot! 🧪
Push blocks to the objective to reach the end of the level, new mechanics are introduced throughout the game adding layers of complexity to the puzzles!

Game Features:
✨ 50 levels to explore
✨ Multiple ways to complete each puzzle
✨ Captivating and challenging gameplay
✨ Simple and accessible controls

Play now! 👇👇👇
🧪https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/sokolab/9n23wfnms054
🧪https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/sokolab-windows/9nmrp8rfccdx
🧪https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP8511-PPSA16081_00-0901951638812986
